3. Bootstrap

B. Sass (.scss) - a CSS extension
// file variables.scss 
$vaiable: red;
ul {
font: Arial
color: $color
}

// Trainslate from scss ->css (Firefox, Chrome cannot understand scss)
> sass variables.scss:variables.css

// Automate change in variables.scss
> sass --watch variable.scss:variables.css

C. Selector

ul > il {
 color: red;
}

ul il {

}

D. Nest css inside css (in sass only)
// css:
// div p {...}
// div ul{...}
// sass:
div {
   p{...}
   ul{...}
}

E. Inheritance (scss)

// share/ inheritance
%message{
   font-family: sanspserif;
   ...
} 

.suscess{
   @extend %message;
   background-color: green;
}

.error{
   @extend %message;
   background-color: red;
}

